BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 28 (KCNA) -- A meeting took place 
in North Hwanghae Province on April 27 in celebration of the 
48th anniversary of the independence of Syria. 
  Invited to the meeting were Syrian Ambassador to Korea Yasir 
Farah, his embassy officials and Syrian students studying in 
Korea. 
  Attending the meeting were chairman of the North Hwanghae 
Provincial Administrative and Economic Committee Yang Man-kil 
and officials concerned and working people in Sariwon. 
  Speeches were exchanged at the meeting. 
  The meeting adopted a congratulatory letter to the Syrian 
president. 

